featureType.abstract:
SeaMap Tasmania: Mapping the seabed for discovery, resource management and biodiversity assessment.
SeaMap Tasmania is a project conducted at the Institute for Marine and Antarctic Studies that aims to improve our understanding of the marine environment and management of marine resources throughout Tasmanian state coastal waters.
